{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/articles/2018/09/11/1546344587216.html","result":{"data":{"asciidoc":{"id":"ac92a93a-35cb-5fc3-a978-29fc386a386e","fields":{"slug":"/articles/2018/09/11/1546344587216.html","birthTime":"2018-09-10T20:58:00.000Z","modifiedTime":"2019-01-01T13:01:00.678Z"},"html":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">Table of Contents</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_在这之前\">在这之前</a>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_1_打开编辑\">1. 打开编辑</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_2_打开虚拟网络编辑器\">2. 打开虚拟网络编辑器</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_3_修改子网_ip\">3. 修改子网 IP</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_4_修改_dhcp\">4. 修改 DHCP</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_5_修改_nat_设置的网关_ip\">5. 修改 NAT 设置的网关 IP</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_6_新建虚拟机\">6.新建虚拟机</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_centos7_安装\">CentOS7 安装</a>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_1_查看网卡配置是否为_nat\">1. 查看网卡配置是否为 NAT</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_2_选择最小化安装\">2. 选择最小化安装</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_3_选择安装硬盘\">3. 选择安装硬盘</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_4_配置网络重点\">4. 配置网络（重点）</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_5_开始安装\">5. 开始安装</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_6_添加密码\">6. 添加密码</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_检查网络\">检查网络</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_问题\">问题</a>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_q忘记了第四步就安装了怎么办\">Q：忘记了第四步就安装了怎么办？</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_qvi_如何保存退出\">Q：vi 如何保存退出？</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_q主机名忘记修改如何修改\">Q：主机名忘记修改如何修改？</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_qping_以后一直跳出_64_byte\">Q：ping 以后一直跳出 64 byte…？</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"preamble\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"sectionbody\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"quoteblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>学习 Hadoop ，第一件事就是需要有 linux 环境，因为他最好的运行环境是\nlinux，而我们的选择，是在服务器端占有一席之地的 centos7\n操作系统。作为老牌稳定的服务器系统，是非常值得我们花时间去学习的。</p>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>环境说明： - 虚拟机：vmware - 操作系统：centos7 - 网络连接：NAT -\n网络配置：静态 ip</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h2 id=\"_在这之前\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">在这之前</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>我们需要稍微配置下 vmware 的 nat （why？为了以后出现问题方便统一纠正）</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_1_打开编辑\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">1. 打开编辑</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.1.png\" alt=\"编辑\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_2_打开虚拟网络编辑器\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">2. 打开虚拟网络编辑器</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.2.png\" alt=\"虚拟网络编辑器\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_3_修改子网_ip\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">3. 修改子网 IP</h3>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>image::https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.3.png[修改子网\nIP]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_4_修改_dhcp\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">4. 修改 DHCP</h3>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>修改 DHCP 设置的 IP 地址段</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.4.png\" alt=\"DHCP 设置\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_5_修改_nat_设置的网关_ip\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">5. 修改 NAT 设置的网关 IP</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.5.png\" alt=\"NAT 设置\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_6_新建虚拟机\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">6.新建虚拟机</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.6.png\" alt=\"新建\">\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"quoteblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>虚拟机的简历过程我就不多赘述。重点在于网络配置</p>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h2 id=\"_centos7_安装\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">CentOS7 安装</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_1_查看网卡配置是否为_nat\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">1. 查看网卡配置是否为 NAT</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.7.png\" alt=\"编辑虚拟机设置\">\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.8.png\" alt=\"查看网络适配器\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_2_选择最小化安装\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">2. 选择最小化安装</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.9.png\" alt=\"最小化\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_3_选择安装硬盘\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">3. 选择安装硬盘</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.10.png\" alt=\"安装硬盘\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_4_配置网络重点\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">4. 配置网络（重点）</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.11.png\" alt=\"点击网络配置\">\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_4_1_configure\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">4.1 configure</h4>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>点击右下角 configure</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.12.png\" alt=\"configure\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_4_2_配置_ipv4\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">4.2 配置 ipv4</h4>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>image::https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.13.png[配置\nipv4]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_4_3_具体配置\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">4.3 具体配置</h4>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>选择方式，设置 ip、掩码、网关、dns，配置完成后，右下角 save</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.14.png\" alt=\"具体配置\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_4_4_开启网络\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">4.4 开启网络</h4>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>获取IP地址（图上多打了一个i），设置主机名，左上角保存</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.15.png\" alt=\"开启网络\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_5_开始安装\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">5. 开始安装</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.16.png\" alt=\"开始安装\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_6_添加密码\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">6. 添加密码</h3>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.17.png\" alt=\"添加密码\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h2 id=\"_检查网络\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">检查网络</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>如果你 <strong>电脑通网的</strong> ，尝试\n<code>ping www.baidu.com</code>，出现如下信息，网络配置成功</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p><span class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.18.png\" alt=\"image\"></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h2 id=\"_问题\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">问题</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_q忘记了第四步就安装了怎么办\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">Q：忘记了第四步就安装了怎么办？</h3>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_解决办法一修改配置文件\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">解决办法一：修改配置文件</h4>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>切换到网卡文件目录 <code>cd /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/</code>，查看目录文件\n<code>ls</code>\n<span class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.20.png\" alt=\"image\"></span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>编辑文件 <code>vim ifcfg-ens33</code>，按下 <code>i</code>\n进入编辑模式，修改`BOOTPROTO=\"dhcp\"` 为 <code>BOOTPRTO=none</code>\n<span class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.21.png\" alt=\"image\"></span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>下方添加如下内容，其中 IPADDR 可以自定义 128-255 区间\n<span class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.22.png\" alt=\"image\"></span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>重启网络，尝试 <code>ping www.baidu.com</code>\n<span class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.23.png\" alt=\"image\"></span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_解决办法二使用命令修改\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">解决办法二：使用命令修改</h4>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>此方法只要一条命令即可，如下</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-shell\" data-lang=\"shell\">nmcli con modify ens33 ipv4.method static ipv4.addr 192.168.112.159/24 ipv4.gateway 192.168.112.2 ipv4.dns 192.168.112.2 connection.autoconnect yes</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>然后重启网络，ping 一下即可</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"literalblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre>systemctl restart network\nping www.baidu.com</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_qvi_如何保存退出\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">Q：vi 如何保存退出？</h3>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_解决办法\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">解决办法</h4>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>当你编辑完成后，按下 <code>ESC</code> ，然后输入冒号 <code>:</code> ，再输入\n<code>wq</code>，即可保存退出。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_q主机名忘记修改如何修改\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">Q：主机名忘记修改如何修改？</h3>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>查看主机名</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p><span class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.24.png\" alt=\"image\"></span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>或者输入 <code>hostname</code></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p><span class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/blog/hodoop/1.25.png\" alt=\"image\"></span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_解决办法一修改配置文件_2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">解决办法一：修改配置文件</h4>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>修改配置文件 <code>vi /etc/hostname</code>,保存退出 <code>:wq</code></p>\n</li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>重启即可</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_解决办法二使用命令修改_2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">解决办法二：使用命令修改</h4>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>使用如下命令</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"literalblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre>hostnamectl set-hostname 主机名</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"2\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>重启即可</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h3 id=\"_qping_以后一直跳出_64_byte\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">Q：ping 以后一直跳出 64 byte…？</h3>\n<div class=\"sect3\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h4 id=\"_解决办法_2\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">解决办法</h4>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>你只要 按下 <code>ctrl + c</code> 即可结束 ping。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","document":{"title":"vmware 安装 CentOS7 + 主机名 + 配置静态 ip"},"pageAttributes":{"category":"归档","description":"vmware 安装 CentOS7 + 主机名 + 配置静态 ip","image":"https://img.hacpai.com/bing/20181215.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1280/h/720/interlace/1/q/100","sort":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/articles/2018/09/11/1546344587216.html","next":{"document":{"title":"vmware 克隆 CentOS7 后 网络配置"},"fields":{"slug":"/articles/2018/09/11/1546344581641.html"}},"previous":{"document":{"title":"eclipse 快捷方式 打开报错"},"fields":{"slug":"/articles/2018/09/09/1546344576907.html"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3069561552","3673333084"]}